  "decision_conditions": [
    "<p>The proposed development, by reason of not providing step free access, fails to provide a fully inclusive and accessible layout and is considered to provide an unsuitable and poor standard of accomodation for potential future residents, contrary to London Plan policies D5 (Inclusive Design), D7 (Accessible Housing), policies LP1 (Design Quality) and LP7 (Housing Design) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 and the Mayors (GLA) Housing SPG.<br></p>",
    "<p>The proposal would result in the unjustified loss of community infrastructure. As such, the proposed development is considered contrary to policy Policy S1 (Development Londonâ€™s Social Infrastructure) of the London Plan 2021 and LP8 (Social and Community Infrastructure) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033.&nbsp;<br></p>",
    "<p>The proposal would provide a non-compliant dwelling mix which would result in the provision of insufficient amounts of family sized accommodation. As such, the proposed development is contrary to policy H10 (Housing Size Mix) of the London Plan 2021 and LP14 (Dwelling Size Mix) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033.<br></p>",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align:top&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;overflow:hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;overflow-wrap:break-word&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-east-asian:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align:baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre-wrap&quot;&gt;The proposed development, by reason of non-compliance with the nationally described space standards, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-east-asian:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align:baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre-wrap&quot;&gt;sub-standard light, outlook and ventilation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-east-asian:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align:baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre-wrap&quot;&gt; and provision of inadequate outdoor amenity space to the proposed residential accommodation would result in the provision of an unacceptable standard of residential accommodation. As such the proposed development is contrary to policy D6 (Housing Quality and Standards) and policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP17 (Housing Design) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 and the guidance contained within the Mayor of London&#x27;s Housing SPG.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
